YVDHOVE::String version 0.01
============================

This module provides some useful "String" functions currently
not available in the default Perl 5.8.x distribution.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Currently no other modules needed

